From: Mike Ragalie <mike.ragalie@shopify.com>
Date: Mon, 3 Sep 2018 10:45:12 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Verify valid shop param

Previously we got this for free, because we would fail to do the
top-level redirect if the shop origin was incorrect. Since we don't get
the check for free anymore, we need to use the same approach as the
`shopify_app` gem and check it against a regex.
